HEADWORD: Storthing
<hw>Stor"thing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Norw.
<ets>storting</ets>; <ets>stor</ets> great + <ets>ting</ets> court,
court of justice; cf. Dan. <ets>ting</ets>, <ets>thing</ets>.]</ety>
<def>The Parliament of Norway, chosen by indirect election once in three
years, but holding annual sessions.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

